HEADWORD: Caffeic
<hw>Caf*fe"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Coffee</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Pertaining to, or
obtained from, coffee.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Caffeic acid</b></col>, <cd>an acid obtained from coffee
tannin, as a yellow crystalline substance,
<chform>C9H8O4</chform>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

